{"id":96988,"type":6,"name":"Star-Crossed","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/d2/6d/96988_V2rM2.jpg","rating":{"total":1,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":0,"7":0,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0},"score":5},"summary":"　　一部类似电影《第九区》（District 9）的外星人题材科幻剧（其实更像《E星恋》），故事创意来自一位西班牙制片人。数百名人形外星人困在地球上，为了防止出现意外，人类决定建立外星人定居点对他们进行集中看管（事实上是种族隔离、集中营）。10年之后，人类决定启动一项特殊的「高中教育项目」，尝试让9名外星少男少女去一所人类的郊区中学读书，看他们是否能融入人类社会。毫无疑问，双方的偏见和生物固有的「竞争意识」让整个计划变得更加复杂，而人类女孩Emery（Aimee Teegarden）和外星男孩Roman（Matt Lante）的恋情可能成为影响人类和外星人和平共存的关键——他们要么成为救世主，要么成为毁掉两个物种的罪人。（简介转自天涯小筑）","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>星恋</li><li><span>别名: </span>星际恋曲</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>跨星之恋</li><li><span>集数: </span>8</li><li><span>开始: </span>2014-02-17</li><li><span>类型: </span>科幻/爱情</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>美国</li><li><span>语言: </span>英语</li><li><span>频道: </span>CW</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>http://www.cwtv.com/shows/star-crossed/</li><li><span>wikipedia: </span>http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Star-Crossed_(TV_series)</li>","collection":{"collect":1,"on_hold":1,"dropped":1},"eps":[{"id":373188,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/373188","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"Pilot","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2014-02-17","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":373189,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/373189","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"These Violent Delights Have Violent Ends","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2014-02-24","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":373190,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/373190","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"Our Toil Shall Strive To Mend","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2014-03-03","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":373191,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/373191","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"And Left No Friendly Drop","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2014-03-10","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":373192,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/373192","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"Dreamers Often Lie","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2014-03-17","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":373193,"url"